    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_outside-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "やっと戻ってきたか。ええと……沙季、大丈夫か？\nさっきから様子が変だぞ？",
      "startTime": 6.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……こほん",
      "startTime": 9.3000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "問題などありません。練習はつつがなく進んでいます\n――全ては絶対勝利のために",
      "startTime": 16.6666678112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "沙季……かわいそうに……疲れてるんだな\n明日の予定、調整しよう",
      "startTime": 25.4973469696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！？\n私、疲れておかしくなった訳じゃないですよ！？",
      "startTime": 29.0666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ～……本人だと様になっているのに\nどうして私が真似すると決まらないんでしょうか……",
      "startTime": 37.499996694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして今のは……スリクスの真似をしてたのか？",
      "startTime": 41.8183450026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "はい……kanaさんとmihoさんの口調を\n真似てました",
      "startTime": 49.2000017803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスのライブ映像を観ていて思ったんです\n彼女達には強烈な個性があるんだって",
      "startTime": 54.9333351136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ映像からだけでは伝わらない、スリクスを\nスリクスたらしめているものを探ろうと思って……",
      "startTime": 62.6666679383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどなぁ……いつもの分析とはまた違う\nアプローチに挑戦したって訳か",
      "startTime": 69.499996376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、franさんのような立ち方や歩き方も\n心掛けてます",
      "startTime": 75.7666679383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だからいつも以上に姿勢がいいのか",
      "startTime": 77.4813835108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "あとは株の変動を見守っていますね",
      "startTime": 80.5147168442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そこも真似してるのか……。沙季、言いにくいんだが\n最近スリクスから苦情がきてたんだ",
      "startTime": 88.4253328924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "えっ。く、苦情ですか？",
      "startTime": 91.325333401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "「沙季がやたらじろじろ見てくる\nなんとかしてくれないか」……ってな",
      "startTime": 97.6725671893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "私、そんなに怪しく見えてたんですか！？\nうぅ……申し訳ないですし、ショックです……",
      "startTime": 104.8333412172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか前も似たようなことがあったな……\nそうだ、千紗だ！",
      "startTime": 114.0434332656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "え？　千紗……ですか？",
      "startTime": 116.143428688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "千紗が大人びた雰囲気に憧れてスリクスを尾行したり\n真似をしたことがあったんだよ。やっぱり姉妹なんだな",
      "startTime": 123.6203899033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、千紗の様子がおかしかった時がありました\nあの子と同じことをしてしまうなんて……",
      "startTime": 133.9666745506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あまり根を詰めると分析もうまくいかないだろ？\n無理はしないでくれ",
      "startTime": 140.2440860081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "ですが……時間は限られていますし\n思いついたことはなんでもやらないと",
      "startTime": 145.2666745506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "私には……それくらいしか取り柄がありませんから",
      "startTime": 147.9925890256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "沙季……なんだかいつもより焦ってないか？\nどうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 155.9644708921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスの皆さんを観察していて分かったんです",
      "startTime": 157.1644708921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "私と彼女達の間には……\nどうしようもないくらい才能の差があるんだって",
      "startTime": 163.1666745506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスのグループ練習を見た時\n何よりもその短さに驚いたんです",
      "startTime": 169.3666735334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "雑談もなく、ごく短時間で仕上げて、あっという間に\n帰ってしまう……月ストの練習とは全然違いました",
      "startTime": 176.6666735334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "私は自主練習をしてからグループ練習に臨んで\n寮に帰ったら練習の映像を見て復習しています",
      "startTime": 186.4333310447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "けれど、スリクスの皆さんは\nそんな風にしていないようでした",
      "startTime": 192.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "確かにスリクスは練習時間が相当短い。星見プロに\n限らず、アイドル業界全体を見てもめずらしいだろうな",
      "startTime": 199.4272248558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "この差を埋めるには……もっともっと徹底的に研究して\n練習するしかないと改めて思ったんです",
      "startTime": 209.1000017804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、いくら同じようにステップを踏んでも\nいくら資料を集めて研究しても……どこか違うんです",
      "startTime": 216.0666735333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "私のダンスはどこか表面的で\n何か根本的なものが掴めていない気がして",
      "startTime": 224.2000200909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
